h3. Summary

When invoking:

{code}
curl --request POST \
  --url https://<instance-name>.atlassian.net:443/wiki/rest/api/content/741966149/pagehierarchy/copy/ \
  --header 'accept: application/json' \
  --header 'authorization: Basic topsecret' \
  --header 'content-type: application/json' \
  --data '{
  "copyAttachments": true,
  "copyPermissions": true,
  "copyProperties": true,
  "copyLabels": true,
  "originalPageId": "<original-page-id>",
  "destinationPageId": "<destination-page-id>"
}'
{code}

where:
originalPageId's title is not altered and apparently has the same title with another page, a HTTP 500 - NullPointerException is returned:

{code}
{
	"statusCode": 500,
	"message": "java.lang.NullPointerException: null"
}
{code}

Expected:
The API should return a valid error message of the actual problem

h3. Workaround
Append:
{code}
{ …, "titleOptions":

{ "prefix": "Foo" }
}
{code}

h3. Summary
Confluence Export fails due to connection with Media Services (the service that handles attachments).
This is impacting all exports: Page export, space export and site backup.

h3. Customer Impact
Unable to generate any type of export.

h3. Expected Results
Backup file is generated and provide a link to download.

